'''哈佛大学绯红队'''（{{lang-en|Harvard Crimson}}）是[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]的体育代表队。学校共有42支队伍参加[[国家大学体育协会|国家大学体育协会]]（{{lang|en|NCAA}}）第一级的各项赛事，参赛数量位居各校之首。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fh/2012-13/releases/2012080853mnlh |title=Women’s Rugby Becomes 42nd Varsity Sport at Harvard University - Harvard |publisher=Gocrimson.com |date=2012-08-09 |accessdate=2015-11-03 |archive-date=2013-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929092318/http://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fh/2012-13/releases/2012080853mnlh |dead-url=yes }}</ref>与其他[[常青藤盟校|常青藤盟校]]一样，哈佛大学并不向学生提供体育奖学金。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hno.harvard.edu/guide/students/stu6.html |title=The Harvard Guide: Financial Aid at Harvard |accessdate=2016-10-01 |archive-date=2006-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060902182731/http://www.hno.harvard.edu/guide/students/stu6.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

